0.1		Initial revision.

0.2		Configuration options: Units of measurement, Calendar.
		Fixed bugs on add/remove events with intervals.
		Unit tests on internal classes.
		Database creation on startup if not found.
		Database upgrade on startup if version is changed.

0.3		Code rewrite to get rid of enterprise patterns.
		Custom CalendarWidget widget.
		Custom Event edit widget.
		Settings are stored not in database anymore but in a
		 platform-depending location.
		New big icons and configurable toolbar layout.
		The database filename has changed: the extension was *.db3, now is
		 "*.db". Please rename the file to have an upgrade at the next
		 program start.
